function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_NEYRELLE_FOLLOWER)
	idNeyrelleDoor = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Frac_Und_03_Neyrelle_Door")[1]
		
	--Neyrelle Bark + Move
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convHoldoutStart, followerNeyrelle)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerNeyrelle)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerNeyrelle, false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerNeyrelle, idNeyrelleDoor, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerNeyrelle, idNeyrelleDoor)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerNeyrelle)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(followerNeyrelle)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idNeyrelleDoor)
end

	idFinalBarrier = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CSD_Frac_Underworld_AncientCity_FinalBarrier")[1]

	Hydra.Wait(2)
